snippet.title: Spark ATS - CGS 2021
snippet.description:
The first mod for one of the best indie platformers, Spark The Electric Jester! Play as Spark in 3 acts + a boss from Sonic After the Sequel.



Check the game as soon as the 18th hits!
https://chaogameshowcase.wixsite.com/cgs2021/games
